Package AI31

Interface AI31Constants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AI31Functions, CardAdder, CustomModeFrame, Human, Machine, MiddleHand, Player, UserInterface, UserPanel
    public interface AI31Constants
    An interface that holds many useful constants for AI31 classes.
    All constants are static and final, meaning they should be referenced by the class name and can never be changed while running.
